角色非常贴合，且有自己的特色。\n\n本科专业是旅游英语，毕业以后做过一阵子导游，后发现自己心底里还是最爱配音，于是走上了配音道路。先是加入网络社团声优之翼（现声创联盟），后与X-ray，老房等人成立了网络配音社团729配音组。2006年开始踏入配音行业。","name":"阿杰","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿傑","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"А Цзе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhang Jie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿傑是中國內地的男性配音演員、配音導演，本名張傑。\n\n北京圈知名配音演員，729 聲工場的創始人。\n\n聲線華麗，配翩翩佳公子一類的男性角色非常貼合，且有自己的特色。\n\n本科專業是旅遊英語，畢業以後做過一陣子導遊，後發現自己心底裏還是最愛配音，於是走上了配音道路。先是加入網絡社團聲優之翼（現聲創聯盟），後與 X - ray，老房等人成立了網絡配音社團 729 配音組。2006 年開始踏入配音行業。","name":"阿傑","primary":false}}]}},"person_116474_translations":{"at":1773513010571,"data":{"id":116474,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kevin Alejandro is an American actor.","name":"Kevin Alejandro","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kevin Michael Alejandro (7 de abril de 1976), es un actor estadounidense.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"케빈 알레한드로","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凱文·亞歷杭德羅","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凯文·亚历杭德罗","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":""